- Bootstrap-created hosted worktree agents are different: `bootstrapConfiguredWorktreeAgents` uses `addWorktreeViaPrimaryInvite(...)` when no local team key. That path creates a hosted invite through the current/primary workspace certificate (`createHostedTeamInviteToken`) and then accepts/connects the new workspace.
